{"tid":1165953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博: 美國考慮制裁5家中國CCTV監控公司","createTime":"2019-05-22T06:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T07:06:07.000Z","uid":227801,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e78247b07b5944cafbd5a40b8bfe44a00e9779e2","tid":1165953,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:36:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.942701/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.942701%2F2&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=e0b2fec7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.942701/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n較早前《紐約時報》引述消息人士報道，美國政府正考慮將中國監控技術公司海康威視(002415.SZ)列入黑名單，限制其購買美國技術的能力。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博通訊社》引述消息人士指，美國正在將包括海康威視在內的多達5家中國公司列入黑名單，禁止他們使用美國的部件或軟件。除海康威視，另一家公司為浙江大華(002236.SZ)，另外三間公司身分未明。(ad/a)"},{"pid":"40e58c2fc1b69712bc36a0ad4f9c52dcbb46f417","tid":1165953,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"陸續有嚟,雜種諗住點樣一個人孭飛？"},{"pid":"78d69c877b9c856b3f39c7ac8133096c76f8ac4f","tid":1165953,"uid":227801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"冇咗人臉辨識技術<br />\n作反咪容易返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501695926da79a7bfebd544416b79b9215992491","tid":1165953,"uid":104833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"Make America  Great Again!!!"},{"pid":"4b0ff92f49bbdc8010ceb4ceebc583549ba7423d","tid":1165953,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"40e58c2fc1b69712bc36a0ad4f9c52dcbb46f417","tid":1165953,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"陸續有嚟,雜種諗住點樣一個人孭飛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"要個小學未畢業既孭飛<br />\n你都幾無良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"